synopsis: On 03/21/2016, a non-UNL affiliate was contacted in the area of N. 16th St. and X St. The individual was found to be extremely intoxicated and transported to The Bridge for further care (.266 BAC).
On 03/20/2016 at approximately 2312 hours, non-UNL affiliate, Kary Nimox, was contacted on a traffic stop near AVP and Q Street. Nimox was cited/released for Driving Under Suspension.
